            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De affectibus et motibus animorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P"/>De affectibus et motibus animo
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>rum capitulum iii .-.-.-.-
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ingenesi. ca. iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e125">subte erit appetitus pec
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>cati / et tu dominaberis illi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. viii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e137">Sensus et cogitatio hu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>mani cordis in malum prona sunt ab ado
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>le scentia sua.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e146">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Oratius epistolarum. libro. primo. epistola. secundum.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e150">Animum rege qui nisi paret 
               <lb ed="#P"/>Imperat hic frenis hunc tu compesce cathenis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Quintilianus de clamationum viii de
               <lb ed="#P"/>clamate</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e162">Quicquid rationem vincit affectus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Seneca in epistolis ad lucillum libro. ix. epistola.
               <lb ed="#P"/>tertia / et fi</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e172">facilius est initia affectuum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>prohibere quam impetum regere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem libro xviiii. epistola. x.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e182">imbecillis est 
               <lb ed="#P"/>primo omnis affectus de se se ipso congitat 
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>et vret dum procidit parat exclu
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>ditur facilius quam expellitur. Quis negat 
               <lb ed="#P"/>omnes affectis / a quodam naturali fluere princi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>pio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e196">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem de remediis fortuitorum. ca. xxi. et 
               <lb ed="#P"/>fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e198">facilius reges animum nulla rerum va
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>nitate tumentem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e206">
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e208">Idem de moribus. hoc habet omnis affectus
               <lb ed="#P"/>ut in quo insanit ceteros furere putet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e221">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ambrosius de officiis libro. primo. ca. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e225">affectus
               <lb ed="#P"/>nature est non potestatis. Et si vis quedam
               <lb ed="#P"/>nature omni appetitu sit tamen idem apetitus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>rationi subiectus est lege nature ipsius
               <lb ed="#P"/>obedit ei.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Boetius in musica. ca. prima.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e241">Ut sese corporis
               <lb ed="#P"/>affectus habent. sic et pulsus cordis mo
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tibus incitantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum libro. vi. epistola. xxviiii. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e253">Ratio motus nostros componat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e259">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Gregorius in pastorali. ca. xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e263">humanum
               <lb ed="#P"/>quidem est in corde tentationem perpeti / de
               <lb ed="#P"/>moniacum vero est tentationis certamie 
               <lb ed="#P"/>in operatione superari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e273">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Isidorus in sinonomia soliloquiorum libro. ii. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e277">in initio resiste cogitatio in pessime
               <lb ed="#P"/>Si titilat prava cogitatio non consenties 
               <lb ed="#P"/>illi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e285">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. capitulo. iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e287">primam peccati suggestionem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>contere ut non sinas eam intuo corde 
               <lb ed="#P"/>manere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-d1e296">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. xxi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d14369-Qd1e298">cohibe animi motus.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
